text: Antonio Chedraui (born 10 June 1966) is a Mexican equestrian. He competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2015 Pan American Games Category:People from Xalapa
